1
00:00:06,010 --> 00:00:07,970
[Please Remember Me Episode 27]

2
00:00:08,100 --> 00:00:08,910
What?

3
00:00:09,550 --> 00:00:11,140
What poison did Xiaoman give my brother?

4
00:00:11,140 --> 00:00:12,340
Is there an antidote?

5
00:00:17,330 --> 00:00:19,420
If your brother got it from me,

6
00:00:20,160 --> 00:00:21,850
it would've been poison for sure.

7
00:00:21,850 --> 00:00:22,910
But Xiaoman didn't

8
00:00:23,490 --> 00:00:24,420
give him poison.

9
00:00:26,040 --> 00:00:27,040
She couldn't do it

10
00:00:27,410 --> 00:00:28,490
because of you.

11
00:00:28,910 --> 00:00:30,270
But your brother said

12
00:00:30,270 --> 00:00:31,550
he'll atone with his life

13
00:00:31,550 --> 00:00:32,710
when the time comes.

14
00:00:33,250 --> 00:00:34,290
It all depends

15
00:00:34,390 --> 00:00:35,640
on his conscience.

16
00:00:36,440 --> 00:00:38,300
It's not you who's in trouble now,

17
00:00:38,510 --> 00:00:39,390
but Nian.

18
00:00:41,240 --> 00:00:43,160
What is Nian hiding from me?

19
00:00:44,820 --> 00:00:46,150
She used her life force

20
00:00:46,730 --> 00:00:49,540
to trade for the power of Bixi to save you.

21
00:00:49,790 --> 00:00:52,150
She may not have much time left.

22
00:00:56,430 --> 00:00:57,550
Not much time left?

23
00:01:01,790 --> 00:01:02,990
How is that possible?

24
00:01:12,510 --> 00:01:13,350
You used Bixi

25
00:01:13,350 --> 00:01:14,750
to save me a few days ago?

26
00:01:16,110 --> 00:01:17,740
Are you affected?

27
00:01:23,590 --> 00:01:24,400
Nian,

28
00:01:25,940 --> 00:01:26,740
I'm sorry.

29
00:01:31,030 --> 00:01:32,160
Is there a solution?

30
00:01:33,870 --> 00:01:35,110
How can I save her?

31
00:01:35,350 --> 00:01:36,710
Can I exchange my life force for hers?

32
00:01:36,710 --> 00:01:37,670
Human life forces

33
00:01:37,670 --> 00:01:38,600
aren't the same.

34
00:01:40,509 --> 00:01:41,370
There's no way.

35
00:01:42,110 --> 00:01:43,190
No way?

36
00:01:46,310 --> 00:01:47,550
How can there be no way?

37
00:01:47,550 --> 00:01:49,610
Aren't you the High Priest of Sushui?

38
00:01:55,000 --> 00:01:56,240
There is one way,

39
00:01:56,550 --> 00:01:58,410
but it's just a legend of our clan.

40
00:01:59,830 --> 00:02:01,160
No one has ever tried it.

41
00:02:01,230 --> 00:02:02,960
I'll try it. I'll try.

42
00:02:04,350 --> 00:02:06,210
The legend says the Xiantang tree

43
00:02:07,070 --> 00:02:08,669
is the sacred tree of Sushui.

44
00:02:08,690 --> 00:02:11,050
Its fruit can bring people back to life.

45
00:02:11,200 --> 00:02:12,590
You used it to save Chief

46
00:02:12,690 --> 00:02:13,520
back then.

47
00:02:14,150 --> 00:02:15,680
Its flower must've fallen.

48
00:02:16,780 --> 00:02:17,620
Yes.

49
00:02:17,990 --> 00:02:19,350
The moment I brought it in front of Grandma,

50
00:02:19,350 --> 00:02:20,280
the flower fell.

51
00:02:20,310 --> 00:02:23,070
But I planted a branch in my backyard, and it's alive.

52
00:02:23,070 --> 00:02:24,470
The flowers are useless.

53
00:02:24,820 --> 00:02:26,750
Only the fruit of the Xiantang tree

54
00:02:26,770 --> 00:02:28,430
can bring people back to life.

55
00:02:28,990 --> 00:02:30,550
But though it blooms every year,

56
00:02:30,550 --> 00:02:31,810
it rarely bears fruit.

57
00:02:32,710 --> 00:02:33,550
Rarely bears fruit?

58
00:02:33,550 --> 00:02:35,110
That means there's still hope.

59
00:02:35,110 --> 00:02:36,640
How can I make it bear fruit?

60
00:02:38,510 --> 00:02:39,450
That sapling

61
00:02:40,040 --> 00:02:41,890
is now bonded to you.

62
00:02:42,180 --> 00:02:43,510
It's said that the tree

63
00:02:43,820 --> 00:02:45,300
can bloom and bear fruit

64
00:02:45,640 --> 00:02:47,040
if watered with blood.

65
00:02:48,430 --> 00:02:49,829
But the tree is sentient.

66
00:02:51,030 --> 00:02:53,630
If the one offering blood harbors ill intent,

67
00:02:54,110 --> 00:02:55,550
it will backfire.

68
00:02:56,320 --> 00:02:58,040
Even if you're righteous,

69
00:02:59,600 --> 00:03:02,070
using your own blood doesn't guarantee

70
00:03:02,730 --> 00:03:04,510
it will bear fruit.

71
00:03:08,190 --> 00:03:10,190
I will make it bloom and bear fruit,

72
00:03:16,430 --> 00:03:18,010
even if I bleed dry.

73
00:03:20,800 --> 00:03:22,370
I have to save her.

74
00:03:25,600 --> 00:03:26,360
Chang Yuan,

75
00:03:28,590 --> 00:03:29,850
keep it a secret for me.

76
00:03:31,790 --> 00:03:32,590
It's open.

77
00:03:32,730 --> 00:03:35,130
Here comes ginseng and black chicken soup.

78
00:03:37,300 --> 00:03:38,220
Take it easy.

79
00:03:38,360 --> 00:03:39,560
Don't burn yourself.

80
00:03:43,350 --> 00:03:44,930
This is ginseng and black chicken soup.

81
00:03:44,930 --> 00:03:46,079
Xiaoman, have more.

82
00:03:46,120 --> 00:03:47,750
It's good for your health.

83
00:03:49,680 --> 00:03:50,760
Thank you, aunt.

84
00:03:55,150 --> 00:03:56,530
This is for General.

85
00:03:56,920 --> 00:03:58,360
General, this is yours.

86
00:03:58,390 --> 00:03:58,950
Come on,

87
00:03:59,420 --> 00:04:00,670
General, try this soup.

88
00:04:00,670 --> 00:04:01,330
It's good.

89
00:04:03,370 --> 00:04:04,240
Aunt Qiu,

90
00:04:04,620 --> 00:04:06,330
aren't you being a bit biased?

91
00:04:07,470 --> 00:04:09,230
From now on, I only have eyes

92
00:04:09,230 --> 00:04:10,970
for Xiaoman.

93
00:04:10,970 --> 00:04:11,550
Aunt.

94
00:04:11,570 --> 00:04:12,690
No General.

95
00:04:14,700 --> 00:04:15,500
Fine.

96
00:04:16,790 --> 00:04:17,600
Okay.

97
00:04:20,630 --> 00:04:21,950
Good stuff.

98
00:04:30,480 --> 00:04:32,450
