101
00:04:35,909 --> 00:04:38,070
It's too early to give us baby gifts.

102
00:04:38,070 --> 00:04:39,600
What are you talking about?

103
00:04:39,840 --> 00:04:41,790
This is for Xiaoman.

104
00:04:43,909 --> 00:04:45,110
Back then,

105
00:04:45,110 --> 00:04:47,270
I had a little sister besides Xiaoshu.

106
00:04:47,820 --> 00:04:48,500
But

107
00:04:48,909 --> 00:04:49,800
our family was poor,

108
00:04:49,800 --> 00:04:51,200
and she passed away early.

109
00:04:51,200 --> 00:04:52,290
Now I see

110
00:04:52,590 --> 00:04:54,710
Xiaoman as my own sister.

111
00:04:55,159 --> 00:04:55,690
This

112
00:04:56,000 --> 00:04:56,930
longevity lock

113
00:04:57,090 --> 00:04:58,650
is for Xiaoman.

114
00:05:00,330 --> 00:05:00,910
Take it.

115
00:05:01,910 --> 00:05:03,070
Thank you, Dashu,

116
00:05:03,420 --> 00:05:06,420
for accepting me as your sister, despite my identity.

117
00:05:06,950 --> 00:05:08,600
What identity?

118
00:05:09,050 --> 00:05:10,810
You're our family now.

119
00:05:10,840 --> 00:05:11,790
Exactly.

120
00:05:15,160 --> 00:05:16,290
This scene is great.

121
00:05:16,470 --> 00:05:18,600
Why don't we draw it?

122
00:05:19,580 --> 00:05:21,160
And name it

123
00:05:23,410 --> 00:05:24,610
the family portrait.

124
00:05:25,130 --> 00:05:26,620
That's a good idea.

125
00:05:26,640 --> 00:05:27,250
What do you think?

126
00:05:27,250 --> 00:05:29,670
Okay. Let's draw it when Xiaoshu is back.

127
00:05:29,990 --> 00:05:30,900
Family portrait, perfect.

128
00:05:30,900 --> 00:05:31,900
Family portrait.

129
00:05:46,820 --> 00:05:47,620
Are you done?

130
00:05:48,310 --> 00:05:49,350
