132
00:05:52,400 --> 00:05:53,490
How is it?

133
00:05:53,990 --> 00:05:54,800
Pretty fast.

134
00:05:55,430 --> 00:05:55,900
You...

135
00:05:57,909 --> 00:05:59,310
You only drew two people.

136
00:05:59,510 --> 00:06:01,080
Art takes time.

137
00:06:02,030 --> 00:06:02,910
Take it easy, General.

138
00:06:02,910 --> 00:06:04,060
Come one by one.

139
00:06:04,830 --> 00:06:06,230
