142
00:06:08,980 --> 00:06:09,620
Okay.

143
00:06:11,000 --> 00:06:12,070
Let's go.

144
00:06:12,100 --> 00:06:12,680
Yes.

145
00:06:12,700 --> 00:06:13,950
Draw General first.

146
00:06:13,970 --> 00:06:14,360
Let's go.

147
00:06:14,360 --> 00:06:15,220
I'm exhausted.

148
00:06:18,350 --> 00:06:19,250
Draw us first.

149
00:06:22,890 --> 00:06:24,530
Let's sit and rest.

150
00:06:41,240 --> 00:06:42,040
General.

151
00:06:42,830 --> 00:06:43,590
Are you done?

152
00:06:43,630 --> 00:06:44,440
Yes.

153
00:06:44,640 --> 00:06:45,440
Next.

154
00:06:47,400 --> 00:06:48,090
Done?

155
00:06:48,130 --> 00:06:50,820
It's my turn.

156
00:06:52,200 --> 00:06:53,880
It's my turn.

157
00:06:54,290 --> 00:06:54,890
You...

158
00:06:55,320 --> 00:06:55,840
Come.

159
00:06:55,860 --> 00:06:57,060
Look at you.

160
00:07:07,570 --> 00:07:08,430
Want an orange?

161
00:07:19,960 --> 00:07:21,620
-Okay, done.
-Are you sleepy?

162
00:07:57,190 --> 00:07:58,510
Okay, done.

163
00:07:58,659 --> 00:08:00,080
Done? Let me see.

164
00:08:00,120 --> 00:08:00,880
All right.

165
00:08:02,520 --> 00:08:03,780
Let me check.

166
00:08:08,940 --> 00:08:10,200
Look how pretty

167
00:08:10,310 --> 00:08:10,900
Xiaoman is.

168
00:08:10,900 --> 00:08:11,430
Is it okay?

169
00:08:11,430 --> 00:08:12,360
Look at her eyes.

170
00:08:13,000 --> 00:08:14,930
Xiaoman is good-looking herself.

171
00:08:15,960 --> 00:08:16,680
Xiaoman,

172
00:08:16,790 --> 00:08:17,930
let's go see it too.

173
00:08:20,340 --> 00:08:21,140
Xiaoman.

174
00:08:27,440 --> 00:08:28,230
Xiaoman!

175
00:08:33,950 --> 00:08:34,740
Xiaoman.

176
00:08:36,840 --> 00:08:37,640
Xiaoman.

177
00:08:38,470 --> 00:08:39,280
Xiaoman!

178
00:08:39,840 --> 00:08:40,760
Xiaoman!

179
00:08:40,809 --> 00:08:41,620
Hurry up.

180
00:08:45,690 --> 00:08:46,490
What's wrong?

181
00:08:49,500 --> 00:08:50,030
She...

182
00:08:50,230 --> 00:08:51,160
She wouldn't...

183
00:08:51,780 --> 00:08:53,310
What are you talking about?

184
00:09:17,180 --> 00:09:18,980
I suddenly fell asleep.

185
00:09:30,620 --> 00:09:31,590
Xiaoman.

186
00:09:36,790 --> 00:09:38,070
What are you doing?

187
00:09:41,150 --> 00:09:43,270
Wealth and longevity.

188
00:09:45,100 --> 00:09:46,760
-It must be good.
-Longevity.

189
00:09:47,570 --> 00:09:48,920
Longevity.

190
00:09:48,950 --> 00:09:49,810
Yes.

191
00:09:51,570 --> 00:09:53,230
I said you two must be blessed.

192
00:09:54,210 --> 00:09:55,450
You both have good fortune.

193
00:09:55,450 --> 00:09:56,490
Is it finished?

194
00:10:00,060 --> 00:10:01,100
Yes.

195
00:10:15,510 --> 00:10:16,320
Chang Yuan,

196
00:10:16,960 --> 00:10:19,020
I can't hold on for much longer, can I?

197
00:10:20,540 --> 00:10:22,470
Have Zisu and the others found out?

198
00:10:22,710 --> 00:10:25,170
Otherwise, why would they act so unusually?

199
00:10:27,430 --> 00:10:28,940
Zisu did come to ask me,

200
00:10:29,710 --> 00:10:30,550
but I...

201
00:10:33,030 --> 00:10:34,560
I didn't tell him the truth.

202
00:10:35,410 --> 00:10:37,210
But he should be able to guess it.

203
00:10:39,340 --> 00:10:40,140
Chang Yuan,

204
00:10:41,980 --> 00:10:44,140
after we resolve the clansmen issues,

205
00:10:44,420 --> 00:10:45,740
take me back to Sushui.

206
00:10:47,950 --> 00:10:49,350
I want to be buried there.

207
00:10:51,790 --> 00:10:52,870
Aren't you going

208
00:10:54,050 --> 00:10:54,850
to tell them?

209
00:10:55,400 --> 00:10:55,980
I...

210
00:10:59,540 --> 00:11:01,450
I have a way to make him forget me.

211
00:11:04,600 --> 00:11:05,660
Princess, please.

212
00:11:12,800 --> 00:11:13,840
Your wound...

213
00:11:14,070 --> 00:11:16,000
Please keep it a secret, Princess.

214
00:11:18,570 --> 00:11:20,630
I see her condition worsening.

215
00:11:22,310 --> 00:11:22,900
Yes,

216
00:11:25,070 --> 00:11:27,000
so I hope she can be happy in the time

217
00:11:28,000 --> 00:11:28,840
she has left.

218
00:11:32,820 --> 00:11:34,940
You two want to sacrifice your lives

219
00:11:35,070 --> 00:11:36,290
for each other,

220
00:11:37,770 --> 00:11:39,170
but have you considered

221
00:11:39,560 --> 00:11:40,910
that the living suffer

222
00:11:40,910 --> 00:11:42,310
more than the dead?

223
00:11:43,730 --> 00:11:44,930
