224
00:11:45,030 --> 00:11:46,430
that whoever survives

225
00:11:46,920 --> 00:11:48,120
will be happier?

226
00:11:49,940 --> 00:11:52,340
I'm learning dream divination technique.

227
00:11:52,710 --> 00:11:54,040
I'll make her forget me.

228
00:11:56,720 --> 00:11:58,950
Love really makes people foolish.

229
00:12:01,430 --> 00:12:02,150
General.

230
00:12:02,570 --> 00:12:03,390
Princess.

231
00:12:05,960 --> 00:12:06,560
Princess.

232
00:12:07,950 --> 00:12:09,540
Nian, are you feeling better?

233
00:12:09,540 --> 00:12:10,650
Much better.

234
00:12:11,270 --> 00:12:12,530
Am I right, Chang Yuan?

235
00:12:13,640 --> 00:12:14,180
Yes.

236
00:12:17,960 --> 00:12:20,130
The moon is so beautiful today.

237
00:12:20,320 --> 00:12:22,080
What should we do?

238
00:12:25,080 --> 00:12:26,200
Anything is fine.

239
00:12:33,590 --> 00:12:36,230
Write a wish on a sky lantern,

240
00:12:36,690 --> 00:12:38,090
and the gods will help

241
00:12:38,280 --> 00:12:39,420
make it come true.

242
00:12:39,510 --> 00:12:41,200
Is this a custom in Lin State?

243
00:12:43,360 --> 00:12:43,860
Here.

244
00:12:46,500 --> 00:12:48,420
So, I can write any wish?

245
00:12:49,010 --> 00:12:49,800
Yes.

246
00:13:16,970 --> 00:13:19,180
Aunt Qiu, good health.

247
00:13:19,370 --> 00:13:22,490
Dashu, good health.

248
00:13:28,990 --> 00:13:29,940
Andâ€¦

249
00:13:31,550 --> 00:13:32,600
And...

250
00:13:33,110 --> 00:13:35,640
General, wealth.

251
00:13:37,800 --> 00:13:39,730
