252
00:13:40,840 --> 00:13:42,910
My wish is...

253
00:13:45,000 --> 00:13:46,610
to be with you now.

254
00:13:47,460 --> 00:13:48,730
For future wishes,

255
00:13:49,360 --> 00:13:50,840
you'll have to help me.

256
00:13:56,850 --> 00:13:58,380
What are you talking about?

257
00:13:58,720 --> 00:14:01,450
For future wishes, we'll achieve them together.

258
00:14:02,580 --> 00:14:03,660
I'm talking about

259
00:14:04,510 --> 00:14:06,510
