260
00:14:07,670 --> 00:14:09,670
What do you think I'm talking about?

261
00:14:12,880 --> 00:14:13,740
No matter what

262
00:14:14,990 --> 00:14:16,250
happens in the future,

263
00:14:16,460 --> 00:14:18,110
we'll achieve every wish

264
00:14:18,140 --> 00:14:19,300
together.

265
00:14:23,880 --> 00:14:25,280
Why did you write so much?

266
00:14:25,290 --> 00:14:27,170
Let's go release them. Hurry.

267
00:14:33,050 --> 00:14:35,020
I still have a wish to write.

268
00:14:35,690 --> 00:14:36,810
Another one?

269
00:14:43,480 --> 00:14:44,280
Wait for me!

270
00:15:13,440 --> 00:15:15,500
Why did you release an empty lantern?

271
00:15:16,230 --> 00:15:17,760
Why didn't you write a wish?

272
00:15:19,050 --> 00:15:21,030
Iâ€¦ I don't know what wish to make.

273
00:15:28,550 --> 00:15:30,500
I want to be with the person I love,

274
00:15:31,440 --> 00:15:33,040
but I don't have a chance now.

275
00:15:34,430 --> 00:15:35,590
Don't you want that?

276
00:15:40,460 --> 00:15:41,850
Do I still have a chance?

277
00:15:43,950 --> 00:15:44,990
Your life

278
00:15:46,400 --> 00:15:47,550
has just begun.

279
00:15:55,030 --> 00:15:56,680
If we were from the same clan,

280
00:15:57,690 --> 00:15:58,820
